Least-crazy end of the line. What matters is humans in my family and local community, in the present generation. Distant strangers, animals and the future are outside the circle (weight 0), so the local option wins. The soup kitchen&#x27;s value is a worked BOTEC — people made happier per dollar times their wellbeing gain, netted against the counterfactual of the money sitting in a bank — and every worldview downstream imports that agreed number unchanged. The pre-EA commonsense baseline; no single EA figure defends it. || Chain: 0 parochial" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJx1Vdtu2zgQ%2FZWB0WLtwHHkdPNQL%2Fxgx8oF626D1N1iEQcILY0kthQpkJQVbZp%2F71ByfYmlpyiemTO3c4YvnRAjlgt7qULsjDpnZzAej2GhGZdgFQSa%2FV%2FSRyFhmZ97wz%2BhUFqEa44FFB50jVUZeD0XtJQUPDEmTzPLlYQgIYwReJAxrYKEM1F5%2BCxIgO3cuAEGd6VN6DviAoES78zmDGzCLLAwNH3QSNVyiQaUrsA0nhI6S9Gi5oZ%2BtwnWif8wEOUyqDD%2BgkClmTJcxjsHipUhEiL9xE2FZiyTIRNKIqQ0DjGAp223%2FvrJlerC8TnDwFLgmokcQUUVwm4wgwpsisbCKi8hd2lcoMH9xkYwVwETYFSewQ9ugwRlHXnt%2F%2BPfTxb%2BDFYlxChRM4uDrPy9AQy5PRjRCRn7IJWtC3FTJKQKa8Y11QoYRe4PjRjd%2BJWOaT6Z5inTJawoRcQDTt99mPpXn%2B996l9v9lUgjxNLo6NpCOU4kfCnemtCxVLplJr46L2Hy1voKk29nqroNGWx5DYPEaafF%2F5lj%2Bpxjf5d9zljorxD%2FdWEMIaXpQTIUGUCb1BkGG4t3sC7cAm9wYXzKVCIFVIl17Q%2BB1G7eMPaxxs6p0DlksgQscDmTEyZ%2FPFvtSXn%2BqEl00kD9Al0h3DaBtdbyteljMODRlwtm3q986VkafTWfF5bqVDG06PY4dZqE3FgrSwfPJphkR0aPGe58DyyFVyEqzw2Bw4XWwfyYEJEeFRzBT4kM2mhUOq4p42DV4PUIn4oZpP5f8DWqJ0SMmL4u8fRPrvCA%2BZZnm7UuWNWoMhIvENp3yiIwtmbQwJZbo0jMLeOS4Fyyh3Dg1vpC9CwcQTLzrGklp0%2BFOG2pRGkyGS3kYs9WvoQXvuHkNd8jbWKRNkMtk8Dh%2BE1YnwjioG7ltSO5raE7uTTVa8Z8YA6zZCT209wBpcbLF9ajRldNMy1SXjWArtPumbYBW3oJk8ZncA5sjjHZqQDgjYjfUnovGRAbUdMI9xp9Z1m2LKOfVo3w30jdtPTYAjDQDepS8zoxhKBQjQtgzzWRMs05%2FMrf9YytTeqadsHGBah2%2Bt9rSO4p4vPdJC01HYktx3wo5OZpmPjXqwxzLmxA42kNYPd6h%2BjtJ2W3VoGfXj5%2BfwTngd7OV57dKJW7gkawwbowXvcqHfR%2BIgtbm6%2F7CQ4gsK9u5ymvfr9kpG4OVVhSIB77yJlcB772Zey8%2FoLmMPV4Q%3D%3D" id="w0"><mxCell style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontSize=11;fillColor=#dfe7ef;s